{"tid":623921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好撚嬲，係地鐵比大媽用BB 車碌腳","createTime":"2018-04-10T11:15:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T11:49:37.000Z","uid":14889,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7112d5093516de1ad4f20ccaf7e00f7a095c33fd","tid":623921,"uid":14889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T11:15:56.000Z","msg":"是咁的，岩先搭地鐵<br />\n有個強國大媽成架BB 車無摺起<br />\n放工時間又多人，佢又坐係最中間個座位<br />\n一到站佢要落車<br />\n就用架BB 車撞出黎<br />\n我係門口位比佢碌到隻腳<br />\n正想屌佢個下<br />\n佢架BB 車碌kick 住咗係條gap 到<br />\n佢起勢咁chok架車<br />\n個BB 就黎跌出黎都唔理<br />\n上車個班人見住個BB 跌出黎<br />\n即刻幫佢抱起個BB<br />\n大媽繼續chok 架車<br />\nChok到個車碌跌埋落條gap 到<br />\n變左三輪BB 車<br />\n到最後開左車，個大媽都無理過BB<br />\n淨係望跌咗落下面嘅車碌<br />\n<br />\n強國大媽一面無奈咁望住個車碌離佢而去<br />\n我心裡怒氣全消<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同隔離個同事一齊恥笑佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9091184d798ec1043756e81e333426b9be865d45","tid":623921,"uid":20396,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T11:17:15.000Z","msg":"上次去迪迪尼 好多大媽推bb車 當自己大撚哂<br />\n一撞到我即刻踢走佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcdd66268d16e12020ecd42f005d423fee1cedab","tid":623921,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T11:49:37.000Z","msg":"原來條毒撚係你"}]}